attributes.title: Does It Do? No Stitch!
attributes.caption: Our Research & Development representatives, Geoff Ramsey & Gavin Free, have scoured the internet & television for products to test and ask the ultimate question: Does It Do?
attributes.description:
Our Research & Development representatives, Geoff Ramsey & Gavin Free, have scoured the internet & television for products to test and ask the ultimate question: Does It Do?
In today's episode, Geoff and Gavin take on the No Stich, a product that claims to hem, mend, and fix anything without sewing! Watch our scientists stress test the No Stitch through rigorous experiments to find out the WWH, the What, Why, and How does it do?
